{"title":"有一句话","authors":["韩庆元"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一句话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韩庆元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地球除了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绕着太阳转以外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主要是自转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就是地球"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一句话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还我两岸猿声飞流三千"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让炊烟温柔地挥手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让小草拔出生命之剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是丰碑不是流水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把史册举高使岁月崛起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土一样清香朴素"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼水衣食一样现实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日出海之鲜艳光彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在决策者们的议事日程上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在乡村小学的读书声里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长城地球脊梁的挺拔里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在香江紫荆花的笑靥里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在港澳台的归心里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将真理将未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形象亲近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让哲学五光十色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族为之而噼啪拔节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下为之而东风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别“社会主义的草”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再生产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高级的无知和愚昧……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅以骨为琴春破冰而出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经半个世纪一个世纪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水火凝炼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自一个人的大悲大喜大思维"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一句话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗啦啦飞作彩虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光灿灿站成灯塔——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设有中国特色社会主义"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}